<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.8">
<l>tuyara mētaru tuṉpa viṉpa viṉaika ḷāyavai yallaṉā</l>
<l>yuyara niṉṟatōr cōtiyā yulakē ḻumuṇṭumiḻn tāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yayara vāṅku namaṉṟa markkaru nañci ṉaiyac cutaṉṟaṉṉait</l>
<l>tayara taṟkuma kaṉṟaṉ ṉaiyaṉṟi maṟṟi lēṉṟañca mākavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for the one who, being without those, [namely] miserable [and] pleasant karmas that bring affliction,</l>
<l>being a light that stands high, swallowed [and] spit out the seven worlds,</l>
<l>the rare poison for Yama’s people who drag wearily, the Unshakable one,</l>
<l>the son of Daśaratha I am withou other as a refuge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
